    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帝国主宰者已将王冠禅让……予其谋杀者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >竞逐主宰就此展开！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款以单位为核心的Roguelike卡组构筑游戏中统领军队：招募训练单位、召唤史诗生物、击败对手，最终直面主宰者本尊。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/125381f9a7470fe95befd7765230db7a.webp?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=59 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/642c6dc1c6a22afe48b67b753092c07a.avif?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从企鹅松鼠到龙族恶魔，各类生物尽可招募，并培养至终极形态。这些形态各异的生物将协同构成独特战略。规划征途、出入酒馆、开启宝箱，通过各类事件强化军队。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/4220e5c0abc17ad09ad5be9d442251c3.webp?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=59 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/642c6dc1c6a22afe48b67b753092c07a.avif?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《竞逐主宰者》中，单位是制胜关键。回合开始时会显示敌人攻击的3片区域，你需在己方回合召唤单位应对。运用战场战术寻找破绽、触发单位间连携组合，在战斗中实时强化队伍并发动酣畅淋漓的连击。别忘了善用遗物拓展战略维度！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/e869602d5f23ce3bab143f7ae41944e7.webp?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=59 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/642c6dc1c6a22afe48b67b753092c07a.avif?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=358 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >召唤特殊的“助陣单位”能提供全局强力增益，甚至改变战场！哪些单位将伴你踏上主宰之路？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044060/extras/078434316a76476ac21d37965c48abdd.webp?t=1772052499\" width=616 height=59 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >易上手难精通的战术玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >200余种具3种专属特性的可招募生物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >60+种可获取的遗物，提供被动增益</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成关卡升级，解锁更多玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断取胜的过程中，逐步揭开“帝国”背后的完整故事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过主宰者等级提升难度，深入探索帝国的更多秘密</p></li></ul>",
